creator: Senseapp Technologies
descriptionHtml:
Never again forget about the products you like! Say goodbye to your messy camera roll full of screenshots, and don't be afraid anymore about losing open tabs in your browser.

Save all the products you like from any online or physical store in one single place. Keep it organised and handy, and buy whenever you are ready!

SAVE ALL YOUR FAVOURITE PRODUCTS IN ONE PLACE

¿Are you shopping in-store? Take a picture and save it instantly in Sense
¿Are you hoping on through multiple stores on your phone searching for the best option? Fear not, share it with Sense from wherever site or app you are and we'll keep it save
¿Have you seen a product you like from desktop? Open our web in your browser and save it directly there

ORGANISE YOUR PRODUCTS IN BOARDS

Keep it simple & handy, ordering your products in boards and categories

CHECK & COMPARE ALL YOUR FAVOURITES

Access your boards & easily compare all your products in one screen. You'll be able to find the most relevant information at a glance, and access further information in the product's page.

WHENEVER YOU ARE READY, BUY WHERE YOU WANT

Through every products' page you will be able to have easy access and get redirected instantly to their online store. If you wish so, we'll also recommend you the closest stores nearby to find the product.

Contact us at: info@senseapp.es

You can also find us at:
Web: www.senseapp.es
Instagram: @ sense.app
Twitter: @thesenseapp
descriptionShort: Save all the products you like in one app

Never again forget about the products you like! Say goodbye to your messy camera roll full of screenshots, and don't be afraid anymore about losing open tabs in your browser.

Save all the products you like from any online or physical store in one single place. Keep it organised and handy, and buy whenever you are ready!

SAVE ALL YOUR FAVOURITE PRODUCTS IN ONE PLACE

¿Are you shopping in-store? Take a picture and save it instantly in Sense
¿Are you hoping on through multiple stores on your phone searching for the best option? Fear not, share it with Sense from wherever site or app you are and we'll keep it save
¿Have you seen a product you like from desktop? Open our web in your browser and save it directly there

ORGANISE YOUR PRODUCTS IN BOARDS

Keep it simple & handy, ordering your products in boards and categories

CHECK & COMPARE ALL YOUR FAVOURITES

Access your boards & easily compare all your products in one screen. You'll be able to find the most relevant information at a glance, and access further information in the product's page.

WHENEVER YOU ARE READY, BUY WHERE YOU WANT

Through every products' page you will be able to have easy access and get redirected instantly to their online store. If you wish so, we'll also recommend you the closest stores nearby to find the product.

Contact us at: info@senseapp.es

You can also find us at:
Web: www.senseapp.es
Instagram: @ sense.app
Twitter: @thesenseapp
descriptionShort: Save all the products you like in one app

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New changes to help you efficiently save all the products you love! What’s new?

- Onboarding: We have optimized the registration process so that you can start using Sense in a comfortable and faster way.

- Brands: Now you can visit the online store of all your favorite brands directly from their profile

We hope you enjoy all the new!

Let’s go!
